headline.main: NEW-YORK CITY.; City Mortality. COURT CALENDAR--MONDAY, JUNE 29.

docs.lead_paragraph: The following in the WEEKLY REPORT OF DEATHS in the City and County of New-York, from the 20th day of June, to the 27th day of June, 1857: Men, 70; Women, 38; boys, 114; girls, 102; total, 324. Adults 108 Children, 216; males, 184; females, 140; colored persons, 8.
